channel.title: InsanityX Client Problem
channel.description:
I have tried to Jar & Sign the insanityX Client but when i try to download the cache on my second laptop it doesn't auto-download.
When i Jar the client its only 550kb where as when i jar another client its around 3mb.
When im on my other laptop i just get "error trying again in 5 seconds..."
I have downloaded the Fixed InsanityX client so they when the client loads up it locates the cache from the C: drive & not from C:\Users\...
How can i fix this problem?
